2026-05-13T22:48:59.9895299Z 12    <!--
2026-05-13T22:48:59.9895676Z 13        Required for reminders to pop as full-screen notifications over the
2026-05-13T22:48:59.9896018Z 14        lock screen when the user enables "Full-Screen Notifications" in
